trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SortResponseControl" /> class is used to pass sort data from the server to the client.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SortResponseControl" /> é usada para passar dados de classificação do servidor para o cliente.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SortResponseControl.AttributeName" /> property contains the attribute name.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SortResponseControl.AttributeName" /> contém o nome do atributo.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SortResponseControl.Result" /> property returns a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode" /> object that contains the result code.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SortResponseControl.Result" /> retorna um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode" /> que contém o código de resultado.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode" /> object that contains the result code.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.ResultCode" /> objeto que contém o código de resultado.
